heroes-battle-arena.description: Multichain Play-and-earn Strategic RPG with zero start investments based on NFTs for the army, magic stones, gods and guilds power. Well known problem of P2E games is the need for significant initial investment. Our game solves this problem with free initial units, low-cost entry payment and a large base of opportunities to increase own income. Our game is based on interaction with NFTs, allowing us to connect the additional project to our game and many blockchains. Our game has 3 types of assets: battle units, magic stones and gods. The gameplay of our game is based on two types of battles: standard and premium. In standard battle, users can set the army on the battleground and look at how to work the auto-battle system. In premium type, users get full control of each step in each battle.

world-of-dypians.description: The World of Dypians (WoD) is a massive multiplayer online role-playing game that is  set in a vast digital environment. Its target audience is individuals who enjoy playing  online games and exploring immersive digital environments. The goals of the game  are to provide players with a rich and engaging experience that allows them to  interact with others, complete quests, and engage in battles. WoD's unique  combination of fantasy and blockchain technology creates an exciting and dynamic  environment for players to explore and experience. The ultimate goal of the game is  to create a virtual world that is alive with activity, where players can form  communities, create their own content, and engage in meaningful interactions with  one another.    World of Dypians is built to support multiple blockchains, making it accessible and  interoperable with a wider audience. We aim to have a sustainable ecosystem where  users can contribute to the growth and development of the world. The multi-chain  integration and the wide range of offerings, including next-gen integrations like other  chains, tokens, NFTs, and a marketplace, make World of Dypians a cutting-edge  solution in the DeFi and metaverse space.
